                                </p>
                                <p><strong>Titular:</strong> CONAEINGEO 2026</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="payment-method">
                                <h3>
                                    <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> Pago en Línea
                                </h3>
                                <p>
                                    Próximamente se habilitará una pasarela de pago
                                    para facilitar el proceso de inscripción con
                                    tarjetas de crédito y débito.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Mientras tanto, también puedes coordinar con la
                                    organización para conocer los medios de pago
                                    disponibles y el procedimiento vigente.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    -->

                    <div class="info-section">
                        <h2>Preguntas Frecuentes</h2>
                        <div class="faq-list">
                            <div class="faq-item">
                                <h3>¿Ofrecen descuentos grupales?</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Sí, se ofrecerán descuentos para inscripciones en grupo.
                                    No obstante, durante la fase de preventa no se aplicarán descuentos, ya que esta etapa cuenta con tarifas preferenciales. La información sobre los descuentos grupales será comunicada oficialmente una vez finalizada la preventa.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="faq-item">
                                <h3>¿Puedo cancelar mi inscripción?</h3>
                                <p>
                                    No. Los pagos realizados no son reembolsables, salvo en caso de cancelación total del evento.
                                    Sin embargo, se permite la transferencia de la inscripción a otra persona dentro de los 3 días posteriores a haber realizado el pago.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-header {
        background: var(--gradient-hero);
        color: var(--color-white);
        padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 80px;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
        color: var(--color-white);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .page-header p {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 3rem auto;
    }

    .registration-info h2 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-top: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .registration-info h2:first-of-type {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .pricing-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin: 3rem 0;
    }

    .pricing-card {
        position: relative;
        text-align: center;
        transition: all var(--transition-normal);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .pricing-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    }

    .pricing-card.featured {
        border: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .pass-visual {
        width: 100%;
        /* Source assets are ~1080x680 (landscape), keep a matching ratio */
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: var(--color-light);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg) var(--radius-lg) 0 0;
    }

    .pass-visual img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: center;
        display: block;
        transform: none;
    }

    .featured-badge {
        position: absolute;
        top: -15px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        color: var(--color-white);
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius-full);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .card-header {
        padding: 2rem;
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        color: var(--color-white);
        border-radius: 0;
    }

    .pass-card.costo-card .card-header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #475569 0%, #64748b 100%);
    }

    .pass-card.costo-card {
        order: 2;
    }

    .pass-card.chachani-card .card-header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f57c3 0%, #1d74e7 100%);
    }

    .pass-card.chachani-card {
        order: 1;
    }

    .pass-card.misti-card .card-header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b9794c 0%, #c98b5d 100%);
    }

    .pass-card.pichu-card .card-header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c45f3 0%, #9a63ff 100%);
    }

    .pass-card.pichu-card {
        order: 3;
    }

    .pass-card.costo-card .price {
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 6.2vw, 2.2rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
    }

    .card-header h3 {
        color: var(--color-white);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .price {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
    }

    .price-note {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .benefits-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .benefits-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: start;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .benefits-list i {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .pricing-card .btn {
        margin: 0 2rem 2rem 2rem;
        width: calc(100% - 4rem);
    }

    .steps-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .step-card {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 2px solid var(--color-light);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    }

    .step-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--color-primary);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .step-number {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        color: var(--color-white);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
    }

    .step-card h3 {
        color: var(--color-dark);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .info-section {
        margin: 4rem 0;
    }

    .payment-info {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .payment-method {
        padding: 2rem;
        background: var(--color-light);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    }

    .payment-method h3 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .payment-method p {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .faq-list {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .faq-item {
        padding: 2rem;
        background: var(--color-white);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    }

    .faq-item h3 {
        color: var(--color-dark);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .faq-item p {
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .page-header {
            padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
        }

        .pricing-cards {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .pricing-card.featured {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        .pass-visual {
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        }
    }
</style>
